- The blue curve represents the interface brane $Q$.
- The red vertical lines and arrows are used to indicate the positions $x_{I}$, $x_{II}$, and $u_{I}$, $u_{II}$.
- Labels for each component are added to match the original image.
- The `decorations.markings` library is used to add arrows to the interface brane $Q$.

